OpenGL ES - texture map all faces of an 8 vertex cube? <p>Working through some OpenGL-ES tutorials, using the Android emulator. I've gotten up to texture mapping and am having some trouble mapping to a cube. Is it possible to map a texture to all faces of a cube that has 8 vertices and 12 triangles for the 6 faces as described below?</p>
<pre><code>// Use half as we are going for a 0,0,0 centre.
width /= 2;
height /= 2;
depth /= 2;
