<p>You need to do the following in your onCreate() after super.onCreate()</p>
<pre><code>titleView = (TextView) this.getViewById(R.id.listTitle);
</code></pre>
<p>Make sure to declare titleView as a field at the top of your class so the rest of your class can access it, if you need to.</p>
