Focus ScrollView On Top Of Page in android <p>I am having an Activity in which I am having some View that is textViews ImageViews and MapView and last is listview on the page.</p>
<p>All these controlls are in a scroll view. The problem is that when the list view populates the scroll scrollview is also scrolls to the listview. The focus is not on the top of page is always on bottom of the page.</p>
