you can do two things to get the same </p>
<p>(1)decrease the height of you views so that they can be fit to actual screen and remove scroll view and defaul scroller of views will work.</p>
<p>(2)intead of list view try to create layout having rows as list view</p>
<pre><code>LinearLayout parent = new LinearLayout(this);
