</code></pre> <p>You probably return <code>null</code> from the <code>getItem()</code> method of your custom adapter, <code>ListviewAdapter</code>(you should add the code for the adapter). Also, there is no need to set the listener on the <code>ListView</code> again.</p>
<p>Modify your <code>getItem()</code> method like this:</p>
