</code></pre> <p>You are getting empty spaces when condition is true? And you want to remove that space? If so, then use <code>View.GONE</code> instead of <code>View.INVISIBLE</code>.</p>
<p><code>View.INVISIBLE</code> make the present view invisible to the user but don't remove the space allotted by it. Thus showing empty spaces between two <code>ListView</code> items.</p>
<p><code>View.GONE</code> not only makes view invisible but also remove that space so that it can be used by others. Thus there will be no gaps between two <code>ListView</code> items.</p>
<p>Change <code>chAppStat.setVisibility(View.INVISIBLE);</code> to <code>chAppStat.setVisibility(View.GONE);</code>.</p>

