<p>any help will be appreciated.</p> <pre><code> In R.layout.list_item layout file if you have any textview then you can set this below code::-
<com.example.TextViewPlus
android:id="@+id/textViewPlus1"
android:layout_height="match_parent"
android:layout_width="match_parent"
