</code></pre>
<p>To update the items in the list view, call <code>getAdapterList()</code> and modify the items in the <code>ArrayList</code> that is returned. After modification, you must invalidate the list by calling <code>notifyDataSetChanged()</code> on the adapter itself.</p>
<p>Hope this points you in the right direction.</p>

