<p>Any help would be appreciated :)</p> <p>So after tons of research, I finally got my tab working. I used the CWAC Merge Adapter which can be found in this <a href="https://github.com/commonsguy/cwac-merge" rel="nofollow">github link</a> for those who are interested.</p>
